snippet.title: Small Super Mario Bros. U Deluxe - RELEASE TRAILER
snippet.description:
*DOWNLOAD HERE:* https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pmUDMfdu2x28WN1GEjBBqgeagG3IdzYj
It's been several years since the original Small U released and we wanted to celebrate that with a brand new and improved version made for Switch.
Finally all of you who only own the Switch version of NSMBU can enjoy my hack.

*Huge thanks for working on this project:*
@DoctorTricky_  - Project Lead
@Rimea - Supervisor

*Great Discord servers for hacking NSMBU:*
